HELP SYS_LOAD_PROJECT_WARNING                        Steve Leach, Jan 05

    sys_load_project_warning( ___________project_dir )

Uses sysprmessage to print a message of the form

    ;;; LOADING PROJECT ___________project_dir

sys_load_project_warning is the default value of the procedure variable
load_project_warning, a call to which is planted by the syntax word
load_project.
